Intesa Sanpaolo’s Board Approves New Remuneration Policies

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-07-20T18:54:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-20/intesa-sanpaolo-s-board-approves-new-remuneration-policies.html
Intesa Sanpaolo SpA (ISP) ’s supervisory
board approved the group’s new remuneration polices, it said in
an e-mailed statement today. The policies include a “new
incentive system” and the introduction of shares, as requested
by the Bank of  Italy , the company said in the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
